ids":[4767,166361,406546,781978,2003653],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"人们对所谓“米池”这一抽卡模式褒贬不一。 有一说一，抽奖这一种模式确实比明码标价更加赚钱，王者也明白无双抽奖比传说限定更加赚钱，而许多游戏厂商也在他们的游戏中放入了抽奖与保底的机制，这里不点名了。 但是，所谓“米池”又为大众所诟病，抽卡虽吸引人，但欧非对比却容易导致人心态失衡。米游三件套从原神一直到绝区零，如今确实需要更大胆的创新。 米哈游作为一个充满创造力的公司，应当研发出新模式来赚钱，现在我们来思考一下，如果你是策划，你觉得新游仍将采用米池吗？如果不是的话，你将研发怎样的新模式？ （ps：米哈游为本人梦中情厂，提此问出于为爱发电，且想集思广益大家的策略）"},"attached_info":"CkAI7pby1OzRwLBsEAMaCTExMDMyMDgwOCDquuC2BjAAOMkBQBRyCTY2NjE5MzI5MngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"3.7 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-79b311650f0dd58bf60da65ac9e9321b_xl.jpg?source=57bbeac9"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"21_1725690071.240270","card_id":"Q_665727221","target":{"id":665727221,"title":"小学一年级孩子做作业拖拉，有什么有效的方法改善？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/665727221","type":"question","created":1725013011,"answer_count":145,"follower_count":255,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[3673693],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"CkAI7pby1OzRwLBsEAMaCTExMDIxNjkzNiCTuMa2BjAAOP8BQBVyCTY2NTcyNzIyMXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"3.6 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-96f41d1bda3b7a3683f4ffc0057bc4f8_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"22_1725690071.240567","card_id":"Q_666278535","target":{"id":666278535,"title":"为什么越是岁数大，越难心动，对爱越难动心？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/666278535","type":"question","created":1725521199,"answer_count":190,"follower_count":280,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[982,3215,4728,9938,22466],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"ex